character_name: Jason Bourne: An amnesiac and former assassin of the CIA's Operation Treadstone.
Pamela Landy: Deputy Director of the CIA and Task Force Chief
Nicky Parsons: A former agent who is taken from her post-Treadstone assignment to assist in the search for Bourne.
Kirill: A Russian Federal Security Service agent and an expert assassin who is working for Gretkov.
Danny Zorn: Formerly assigned to Treadstone headquarters
Jarda: A former Treadstone operative based out of Munich.
Irena Neski: Daughter of politician Vladimir Neski
